    <item>
      <title>上田沉默期最长 市场对利率充满猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/ueda-s-longest-silence-period-keeps-market-guessing-over-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫创下了政策会议前沉默时间最长的个人纪录，这使得利率决定更加难以预测，并增加了金融市场的波动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/ueda-s-longest-silence-period-keeps-market-guessing-over-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 04:54:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>截止日期临近，哈里斯专注于副总统候选人的搜寻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/harris-focuses-on-vice-presidential-search-as-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有望成为民主党候选人的副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 已开始审查潜在的竞选搭档，因为她面临着在通过网络点名完成党内选举之前的紧迫期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/harris-focuses-on-vice-presidential-search-as-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 04:17:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国制造的欧洲电动汽车对欧洲汽车制造商构成新威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/china-electric-vehicle-companies-expand-in-europe-to-ease-eu-tariff-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从西班牙到土耳其的工厂都准备为中国企业生产汽车，以避开巨额的新进口关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/china-electric-vehicle-companies-expand-in-europe-to-ease-eu-tariff-pain</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 04:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚新任总理为保障安全采取紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/estonia-s-new-premier-brings-in-austerity-for-the-sake-of-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波罗的海国家新任总理克里斯汀·米卡尔表示，如果爱沙尼亚想加强安全以抵御俄罗斯的威胁，那么该国别无选择，只能忍受进一步增加税收并减少国家开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/estonia-s-new-premier-brings-in-austerity-for-the-sake-of-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡即将举行选举，国际货币基金组织交易员寻求授权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/sri-lanka-to-vote-for-president-as-imf-negotiator-seeks-mandate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡将于 9 月举行选举，选出新总统，现任领导人拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈 (Ranil Wickremesinghe) 寻求获得授权推行严格的财政改革，以使这个南亚国家摆脱有史以来最严重的金融危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/sri-lanka-to-vote-for-president-as-imf-negotiator-seeks-mandate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 03:15:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰敦促香港不要帮助俄罗斯绕过制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/ukraine-urges-hong-kong-to-stop-russia-from-bypassing-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国政府高层官员罕见会晤中，乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库列巴要求香港特首李家超采取措施，防止俄罗斯及其企业利用香港规避制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/ukraine-urges-hong-kong-to-stop-russia-from-bypassing-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 02:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
